title._content: Couple of guys, better known as Harry Bondy and Judge Lovelee

description._content: Title: Harry Bondy and Judge Lovelee-0211201194311 Image Description: "Judge" George G. Lovelee was a shipping clerk at the Lebanon Paper Mills for fifteen years. He served as county sealer of weights and measures for two years and for six years he was deputy county assessor. Lovelee was the justice of the peace in Lebanon for ten years, resulting in his becoming known as "Judge" Lovelee.
